            "answer": "<p>SoundOff Signal offers a full lineup of emergency lighting, including LED light bars, surface mounts, grille lights, interior visor lights, beacons, perimeter lighting, and traffic advisors. Their nROADS and mpower® series are especially popular for police, fire, EMS, and utility applications, combining sleek designs with high-output performance.</p>",
