            "answer": "<p>Yes. SoundOff Signal lights are designed to be vehicle-agnostic and work with most makes and models. They offer universal mounting options and various sizes to fit everything from compact patrol units to full-size trucks. For fleet-specific setups, SoundOff also offers vehicle-specific brackets and mounting kits.</p>",
            "icon": "none"
