            "question": "How does SoundOff Signal’s nROADS technology improve visibility?",
            "answer": "<p>nROADS (Narrow Reflector Optic And Diode System) uses precise reflector optics to focus and direct LED light more efficiently. This results in sharper intensity, wider horizontal spread, and reduced glare, making emergency vehicles more visible at greater distances and sharper angles, especially in complex traffic situations.</p>",
            "icon": "none"
          }
        },
