            "answer": "<p>LED lights from SoundOff Signal are significantly brighter, more energy-efficient, and longer-lasting than halogen lights. LEDs turn on instantly, don’t require warm-up time, and are solid-state, meaning fewer parts to break or burn out. Halogen lights are outdated by comparison, with shorter lifespans and higher power draw.</p>",
            "icon": "none"
